subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which emperor founded the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के श्रीमद् प्रभु कौन सीते?
explanation_en: Pratap Singh is the founder of Jaipur. He built the city in 1727 and named it after his victory in the battle of Haldighat against Maharaja Jai Singh II.
